'''Oregon Bar''' is a former settlement in [[Butte County, California|Butte County]], [[California]]. It was located on the West Branch of the [[Feather River]] below [[Nelson Bar, California|Nelson Bar]].<ref name=CGN>{{California's Geographic Names|284}}</ref> It is now under [[Lake Oroville]].<ref name=CGN />

